      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $P_n = (X-2)^{2n} + (X-1)^n - 1$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n = (X-2)^{2n} + (X-1)^n - 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "da4d1810-9196-489d-9e80-b8829323faab",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $P_n$ est divisible par $X-1$ et par $X-2$.\n    On note $Q_1$ et $Q_2$ les quotients correspondant.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n\\)</span> est divisible par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X-1\\)</span> et par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(X-2\\)</span>. On note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Q_1\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Q_2\\)</span> les quotients correspondant.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4f6c37d7-65bc-4418-96c5-7a5f50536183",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que $P_n$ est divisible par $(X-1)(X-2)$ et que le quotient est $Q_2-Q_1$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P_n\\)</span> est divisible par <span class=\"math inline\">\\((X-1)(X-2)\\)</span> et que le quotient est <span class=\"math inline\">\\(Q_2-Q_1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "16c2a9b0-9cfb-4d72-a9d6-797cc27bbbfc",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que ce quotient est {\\'e}gal {\\`a} :\n    $$\\Bigl((X-2)^{2n-2} - (X-2)^{2n-3} + \\dots - (X-2) + 1\\Bigr)\n    + \\Bigl((X-1)^{n-2} + (X-1)^{n-3} + \\dots + (X-1) + 1\\Bigr).$$",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que ce quotient est <span>é</span>gal <span>à</span> : <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\Bigl((X-2)^{2n-2} - (X-2)^{2n-3} + \\dots - (X-2) + 1\\Bigr)\n    + \\Bigl((X-1)^{n-2} + (X-1)^{n-3} + \\dots + (X-1) + 1\\Bigr).\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "33a40184-67e6-4f67-9cad-ab89adef3109",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Faire le produit.",
        "html": "<p>Faire le produit.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
